OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUN warns against 'vampiric'
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fglobal water use           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A United Nations report has warned of a
OL,6, looming global water crisis and an     
OL,7, "imminent risk" of shortages due to    
OL,8, overconsumption and climate change.    
OL,10,FThe world is "blindly travelling a     
OL,11,Fdangerous path" of "vampiric           
OL,12,Foverconsumption and overdevelopment",  
OL,13,Fthe report says.                       
OL,15,FIts publication comes before the first 
OL,16,Fmajor UN water summit since 1977.      
OL,18,FThousands of delegates will attend the 
OL,19,Fthree-day gathering in New York which  
OL,20,Fbegins on Wednesday.                   
